OL,3,CNeurodiverse mum fears further debt as
OL,4,Cenergy prices set to rise again
OL,6,FSince the cost of energy crisis began
OL,7,Ftwo years ago, a mum from Sussex, who
OL,8,Fis neurodiverse, has struggled
OL,9,Ffinancially.
OL,11,FAshley Desmond from Brighton has ADHD
OL,12,Fand other medical conditions,
OL,13,Fincluding fibromyalgia and chronic
OL,14,Ffatigue, which require her to stay
OL,15,Fwarm.
OL,17,FIt has meant her energy bills have
OL,18,Fquadrupled, since costs started to
OL,19,Frise, which has forced her to take out
OL,20,Floans to keep her family fed and
OL,21,Fclothed.
