OL,3,CNeurodiverse mum fears further debt as
OL,4,Cenergy prices set to rise again
OL,6,FShe now fears getting into further
OL,7,Fdebt after news that energy bills are
OL,8,Fset to rise again.
OL,10,FOfgem's announcement means the average
OL,11,Fhousehold energy bill is to increase
OL,12,Fby 10% from October as the price cap
OL,13,Fis set to increase.
OL,15,FAshley Desmond said: "I was only just
OL,16,Fstarting to get out of debt from when
OL,17,Fit went up the first time. My gas and
OL,18,Felectric was #120 a month and, within
OL,19,Fa year, it was #400 which was a huge
OL,20,Foverwhelming leap for me.
