OL,3,CNeurodiverse mum fears further debt as
OL,4,Cenergy prices set to rise again
OL,6,F"I have ADHD so dealing with letters
OL,7,Fand finances is really difficult for
OL,8,Fme.
OL,10,F"It ended up that I had to get payment
OL,11,Fplans for anything extra like
OL,12,Fchildren's clothes, school trips, car
OL,13,Fbreaking down.
OL,15,F"I just had to put on loans, which I
OL,16,Fdon't normally do, so I ended up
OL,17,Fgetting into a lot of debt."
