OL,3,CNeurodiverse mum fears further debt as
OL,4,Cenergy prices set to rise again
OL,6,FMs Desmond says she spent the last six
OL,7,Fmonths creating spreadsheets, and will
OL,8,Fnow need to recalculate her finances,
OL,9,Fwhich she says for someone with ADHD
OL,10,For autism can send them into a
OL,11,Fmeltdown.
OL,13,FShe continued: "Not just the change to
OL,14,Fheat and electric, but (people who are
OL,15,Fneurodiverse) find it harder to juggle
OL,16,Fbills and emails.
OL,18,F"It can really set us back, for those
OL,19,Fof us that struggle with self-
OL,20,Fmanagement.
