OL,3,CNeurodiverse mum fears further debt as
OL,4,Cenergy prices set to rise again
OL,6,F"If we need help, we need to fill out
OL,7,Fmore forms and emails... so having to
OL,8,Freach out for more help is something
OL,9,Fthat would set us back even further."
OL,11,FThe energy industry regulator Ofgem
OL,12,Fsays high prices are not going away
OL,13,Fany time soon.
OL,15,FEd Miliband, Energy Secretary, said:
OL,16,F"The only solution to get bills down,
OL,17,Fand greater energy independence is the
OL,18,FGovernment's mission for clean, home-
OL,19,Fgrown power.
