OL,3,CNeurodiverse mum fears further debt as
OL,4,Cenergy prices set to rise again
OL,6,F"That's why we have hit the ground
OL,7,Frunning, lifting the onshore wind ban,
OL,8,Fconsenting unprecedented amounts of
OL,9,Fsolar power and setting the largest-
OL,10,Fever budget for our renewables auction.
OL,12,F"We will also do everything in our
OL,13,Fpower to protect bill payers,
OL,14,Fincluding by reforming the regulator
OL,15,Fto make it a strong consumer champion,
OL,16,Fworking to make standing charges
OL,17,Ffairer, and a proper Warm Homes Plan
OL,18,Fto save families money."
